      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 47
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner. This car is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve been super meticulous about keeping it spotless and staying on top of every single service. It drives like an absolute dream and is just waiting for a new home. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it! I'm happy to chat or show you around the car whenever you're free!",
      "price": 43900.0,
