    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is an exceptional E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54B32 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS for a razor-sharp 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission delivers tactile engagement, paired with a factory M-Variable differential lock. Mechanically flawless, it has received proactive rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement. The chassis remains rigid, and the suspension geometry is perfectly dialed. This is a turn-key, high-revving masterpiece for the discerning purist.",
